Phases
======
1) Workspace
2) Staging / Index
3) Local repo

------------------
touch file1
ls

touch file2 file3
ls

mkdir dir1
ls

mkdir dir2 dir3
ls

===============================
touch file1
ls
git status
git add file1 (workspace to staging)
git status
git commit -m "label" file1  {staging to local repo)
git status
git log
git show

===========================
touch file2 file3 file4
ls
git status
git add file2 file3 file4
or
git add .
or
git add *
or
git add -A

git status
git commit -m "label"
git status
git log


